sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller
    participant Parent as Parent Agent Loop
    participant Child as Child Workflow Tool Boundary
    participant PEP as Azure Function PEP
    participant Logs as Azure Monitor Logs Connector
    participant LAW as Log Analytics Workspace

    Caller->>Parent: Request Sentinel health check
    Parent->>Child: Call workflow in this logic app
    Child->>PEP: POST fixed tool contract<br/>Managed Identity + Entra ID
    PEP-->>Child: allow / deny decision
    alt allow == true
        Child->>Logs: Run fixed approved query
        Logs->>LAW: Query SecurityIncident
        LAW-->>Logs: Query response
        Logs-->>Child: Results
        Child-->>Parent: Success response
        Parent-->>Caller: Response
    else deny or failure
        Child-->>Parent: Fail-closed response
        Parent-->>Caller: Denial / unavailable
    end
